Integration experience with using SOAP / REST and scripted APIs. Experienced with implementing SAML 2.0 integration, eBonding integrations. Experienced in translating business processes into custom workflows to support Service Catalog requests enabling automation of request fulfillment. Experience building scoped applications with ServiceNow Studio.
